200
00:13:31.583 --> 00:13:35.546
Saya harap kami ada ubat
untuk Pompe, tetapi tiada.


201
00:13:36.673 --> 00:13:37.716
Saya minta maaf.

202
00:13:41.345 --> 00:13:42.263
Lihat, mungkin...

203
00:13:43.432 --> 00:13:45.643
