01:29:05.566 --> 01:29:08.028
- Bob!
- Jangan terlalu berharap.


1326
01:29:11.449 --> 01:29:12.700
Semuanya bergantung
pada nasib.


1327
01:29:43.910 --> 01:29:44.828
Kuek!

